Output ONLY valid JSON (no markdown fences, no commentary). Use these exact fields:

{
  \"docs_updated\": [{\"file\": \"path/to/doc.md\", \"changes\": \"brief description of what was updated\"}],
  \"docs_unchanged\": [\"files checked but not needing updates\"]
}"

